      <title>Permira 考虑出售德国化学品公司 CABB</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/permira-is-said-to-consider-sale-of-german-chemicals-firm-cabb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，收购公司 Permira 正在考虑以超过 10 亿欧元（10.6 亿美元）的价格出售特种化学品制造商 CABB，此前该公司在瑞士上市的计划未能于 2022 年实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/permira-is-said-to-consider-sale-of-german-chemicals-firm-cabb</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:08:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
